02:31.360 --> 02:34.591
Hey, I got it. Go over there
and punch that dude right in the face.

02:34.800 --> 02:36.472
Which dude?

02:36.680 --> 02:37.874
-That dude?
-Yeah.

02:38.080 --> 02:40.435
No way. He'd kick my ass.

02:41.360 --> 02:42.839
True that.

02:44.080 --> 02:47.277
-This is so hard, you know?
-Yeah.

02:49.960 --> 02:51.439
I know.

02:51.680 --> 02:53.398
It's simple.

02:53.720 --> 02:57.872
If you ask a cop if he's a cop,
he's, like, obligated to tell you.

02:58.080 --> 02:59.877
It's in the Constitution.

03:00.080 --> 03:02.116
Constitution of America?

03:04.280 --> 03:06.874
So go ahead and ask.

03:07.080 --> 03:09.275
-You a cop?
-No, no. Not like that.

03:09.480 --> 03:11.516
Ask it, like, official.

03:11.720 --> 03:14.188
Are you a police officer?

03:14.720 --> 03:18.110
No, I am not a police officer.

03:18.320 --> 03:21.232
Okay, then. Hundred
and seventy-five for a teenth.

03:22.240 --> 03:24.117
The price is the price, yo.

03:28.400 --> 03:29.992
All right.

03:54.520 --> 03:57.193
There you go. Enjoy.

03:58.080 --> 03:59.718
Thanks, man.

04:05.600 --> 04:08.433
Albuquerque Police!
You're under arrest! Get on the ground!

04:08.640 --> 04:12.918
Get on your stomach now!
On your stomach! Get on the ground!

04:13.960 --> 04:16.872
Hold it right there. Don't move.
Stay down.

04:37.240 --> 04:41.916
I had a good job
until my boss accused me of stealing.

04:43.080 --> 04:44.957
I'd better call Saul!

04:48.000 --> 04:51.231
I was out partying,
minding my own business....

04:52.600 --> 04:55.956
-You are under arrest.
-I'd better call Saul!

04:56.840 --> 04:57.875
Hi, I'm Saul Goodman.

04:58.080 --> 04:59.718
Did you know that you have rights?

04:59.920 --> 05:02.275
The Constitution says you do.
And so do I.

05:02.480 --> 05:04.357
I believe that until proven guilty...

05:04.560 --> 05:07.597
...every man, woman,
and child in this country is innocent.

05:07.800 --> 05:09.677
And that's why I fight for you,
Albuquerque.

05:09.880 --> 05:10.835
Better call Saul.

05:11.040 --> 05:13.031
Saul Goodman, attorney at law,
505-164-CALL.

05:13.240 --> 05:16.118
That's 505-164-CALL.

05:17.760 --> 05:21.275
I really need to get some furniture.

05:22.560 --> 05:23.959
I suggest you start with a bed.

05:27.240 --> 05:29.674
God, I wish we could smoke in here.

05:29.880 --> 05:33.077
-Well, you can't.
-Yeah, no. I know.

05:33.280 --> 05:35.191
I'm just saying.

05:37.520 --> 05:39.272
Don't think I can't smell that weed.

05:39.480 --> 05:41.277
You better seriously hope
that airs out.

05:41.480 --> 05:44.119
My dad will keep
your security deposit.

05:45.280 --> 05:48.431
He has a nose
like a damn bloodhound.

05:48.640 --> 05:50.198
Yeah?

05:50.400 --> 05:54.439
Has he ever caught you?

05:55.360 --> 05:59.069
