07:44.360 --> 07:45.952
We....

07:46.280 --> 07:47.793
We cool?

07:51.200 --> 07:52.713
Your satellite is on, by the way.

07:56.120 --> 07:58.156
That screen is badass.

08:11.880 --> 08:13.871
