so there's a bright side.

08:28.960 --> 08:31.235
So when the laziest boy
in the world wakes up...

08:31.440 --> 08:33.317
...tell him he better wash
those sneakers.

08:33.520 --> 08:34.475
And I said bye.

08:34.679 --> 08:36.909
