09:26.080 --> 09:29.470
Hey, Marie. It's me. What's up?

09:35.880 --> 09:38.440
Yesterday I got home
and found him.

09:39.080 --> 09:41.469
He didn't even tell me
he was coming.

09:41.960 --> 09:45.236
-A man was killed?
-A Federale, right in front of him.

09:46.120 --> 09:49.351
