"I'm fine. I'm fine. Leave me alone."

10:36.760 --> 10:38.352
Baby, not now.

10:39.600 --> 10:42.398
It's-- It's me, Hank. Sorry.

10:46.080 --> 10:47.957
Hey, buddy. What's...?

10:48.160 --> 10:49.639
What's up?

10:51.920 --> 10:53.399
I just....

10:53.840 --> 10:55.876
Do you mind if l...?

10:56.160 --> 10:57.991
