with somebody?

12:29.680 --> 12:32.592
What, a shrink?
No, no, no. Can't go down that road.

12:32.800 --> 12:35.394
Start going down that road,
kiss your career goodbye.

12:36.280 --> 12:41.991
Or Marie. Or me, if you like.

12:48.000 --> 12:51.959
You know, I don't know
how to say this. I....

12:53.880 --> 12:55.871
You know, the things I deal with...

12:57.040 --> 13:00.157
...you and me don't have much of a--

13:00.360 --> 13:04.239
What you might call
"an experiential overlap."

13:12.160 --> 13:14.469
What if I told you we do?

13:21.680 --> 13:25.958
I have spent my whole life scared.

13:27.920 --> 13:30.912
Frightened of things
that could happen...

13:31.120 --> 13:33.350
...might happen, might not happen.

13:33.560 --> 13:36.916
