16:38.560 --> 16:40.118
Badger got busted.

16:40.320 --> 16:42.038
He's in jail.

17:17.960 --> 17:20.190
Honey, I'm home!

17:20.400 --> 17:22.516
Too slow! What's up?

17:22.720 --> 17:24.438
Got more lives than a damn cat.

17:24.640 --> 17:26.517
Now if I could only learn
to lick myself.

17:27.520 --> 17:30.671
