18:08.480 --> 18:10.835
...if they come across
that famous blue meth of yours.

18:11.040 --> 18:13.395
Sure enough, last night.

18:13.600 --> 18:15.909
Got themselves
an honest-to-God dealer.

18:16.120 --> 18:19.271
I was thinking of cruising over
and saying hello.

18:20.000 --> 18:21.399
Maybe you'd like to go with me?

18:22.480 --> 18:24.755
Yeah. Well, all right.

18:25.520 --> 18:27.636
