18:33.720 --> 18:35.950
You like Badger or Brandon?

18:36.760 --> 18:41.038
I like people who don't, like,
abuse the Constitution.

18:41.240 --> 18:42.355
Badger, listen.

18:42.960 --> 18:44.234
Hey.

18:44.640 --> 18:46.870
I'm trying to help you here, man.

18:47.400 --> 18:51.552
